EBOOK\u2019S HARASSMENT PROBLEM<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17879d6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"17879d6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>The issue:<\/strong> Facebook\u2019s harassment guidelines are very weak, especially when it comes to Sexism and non-consensual images.\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-047db2a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"047db2a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>The intervention:<\/strong> Level Up partnered with the Sunday Times on an investigation into Facebook\u2019s failure to deal with sexism on its platform, finding that half of all women had experienced abuse. Level Up members also mass-reported the group \u2018Women Who Eat On Tubes\u2019, crashed Facebook\u2019s Carnaby St popup to grill staff on their lack of care for female users and Level Up secured meetings with a Facebook executive.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac15a77 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ac15a77\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>The impact:<\/strong> Level Up\u2019s investigation had media coverage across the board from the Sunday Times to the Sun, which helped the team secure meetings with a Facebook executive, and advocate for a stalking survivor.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ad1c280 elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"ad1c280\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/levelup.yourmovement.org\/p\/sexual-violence-in-football\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">SIGN THE PETITION<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48a1c7a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"48a1c7a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c1d3938 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c1d3938\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4fd6958 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4fd6958\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d4f1bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6d4f1bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/7.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2524 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcs